            &lt;/key&gt;
            &lt;one-to-many class=&quot;path.to.class.Middel&quot; /&gt;
        &lt;/set&gt;
        ...

As inverse is set to â€trueâ€, it means â€œMiddleâ€ class is the relationship owner, so Principal class will **NOT UPDATE** the relationship.

